...the tree, who had taken pity on the ego that was Rob. Rob blushed and went off to fix his make-up in the toilets so that he did not look like a complete fool. The others thanked the tree and informed of their quest to first get Rob some modesty or someone would kill him before midnight. The tree said he was sure that it would be a sad loss for someone if Rob was to perish but that he probably would have brought it on himself. No-one disagreed with this. Suddenly there was a bump and the tree anounced that they had arrived on Spooky Island. All looked around in amazement and were about to get off the boat when...